lead_paragraph: A clash between supposedly the two most expensive lineups in history overseen by two of the most decorated coaches will end the phoney war and ignite the Premier League season for real when Manchester United host Manchester City on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: United and City Clash Set to Ignite Season
